<br>
This cleric was in an established guild, so I spoke to one of the guild leaders.  I mean really, who cares about the actual piece, but that sort of behaviour is just so very uncool.  The leader agreed, and said she would talk to him.  He denied it, said he was trading them for a friend.  So she told me flat out that she was going to take his word for it, in spite of the conversation in EC, etc.<br>
<br>
